Befestigungsklammern: White - P0A
Verbinderposition: außenliegend</text>
	<text lang='en'>Type: Screen
Application: Single sided desk
Foam: With foam
Screen width (mm): 1200
Screen fabric material: Upholstery - U
Fabric group: Fabric group F
Fabric range: Atlantic - (Gabriel)
Fabric colours: Pebble - AT61
Bracket finish: White - P0A
Connector position: Out</text>
	<text lang='fr'>Type: Panneau
Application: Poste individuel
