      <description type='features' default='0'>
	<text lang='de'>Schrankbreite (mm): 800
Schrankhöhe (mm): 720
Türenmaterial: Melamin 18 mm ohne Holzmaserung
Abdeckplatte - Material: farbiges Metall
Korpusfarbe: White - P0A
Türenfarbe / - dekor: White Melamine - HL9
Grifffarbe: White - P0A
Abdeckplatte - Farbe: White - P0A</text>
	<text lang='en'>Cabinet width (mm): 800
Cabinet height (mm): 720
Door material: Plain Melamine 18 mm
Top material: Painted Metal
Carcass paint finish: White - P0A
Door wood finish: White Melamine - HL9
Handle paint finish: White - P0A
Top paint finish: White - P0A</text>
	<text lang='fr'>Largeur armoire (mm): 800
Hauteur armoire (mm): 720
Matériaux portes: Mélamine unie 18 mm
Matériaux du dessus: Métal peint
Finition corps: White - P0A
Finition portes: White Melamine - HL9
Finition poignée: White - P0A
Finition dessus: White - P0A</text>
	<text lang='it'>Larghezza cassero (mm): 800
Altezza cassero (mm): 720
Materiale ante: Melaminico tinta unita 18 mm
Materiale del top: Metallo verniciato
Finitura verniciata del cassero: White - P0A
Finitura decoro legno delle ante : White Melamine - HL9
Finitura verniciata della maniglia: White - P0A
Finitura verniciata del top: White - P0A</text>
      </description>
